<section class="sect" id="solution">
  <div class="wrap">

    <p class="sect-eyebrow" data-reveal>The Solution</p>
    <h2 class="sect-heading" data-reveal>Native gem management<br />without the overhead.</h2>
    <p class="sect-body" data-reveal>
      Pack talks directly to RubyGems.org. No Ruby interpreter, no Bundler.<br />
      Just fast, parallel gem installation with sub-millisecond lockfile parsing.
    </p>

    <div class="code-preview" data-reveal>
      <pre><code><span class="comment"># Install gems in seconds, not minutes</span>
$ pack install
Installing 47 gems... <span class="success">done</span> <span class="muted">in 2.3s</span>

<span class="comment"># Parse lockfile instantly</span>
$ time pack lock
<span class="success">15µs</span>

<span class="comment"># Start Rails server immediately</span>
$ pack server
<span class="muted">Pack v0.1.0 — Rails 8.0.0</span>
<span class="success">Server running on http://localhost:3000</span></code></pre>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sect {
    padding: var(--sp-24) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sect-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .sect-heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-3xl));
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .sect-body {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-12);
  }

  .code-preview {
    background: var(--bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--sp-6);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-preview pre {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .code-preview code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fg);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .code-preview .comment { color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .code-preview .success { color: var(--green); }
  .code-preview .muted { color: var(--fg-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .code-preview { padding: var(--sp-4); }
    .code-preview code { font-size: var(--text-xs); }
  }
</style>
